      <p>Hi Molly &#8211; I just read your last post while coming to this site for this recipe. I made it the Christmas after it was posted, and I wanted to make it again this year. Like you I&#8217;ve had a lot of changes in the years in between, life focus has changed, loved ones have been lost.  It is one of the best things about food &#8211; which is basically the theme of your food writing &#8211; that food is a constant in an ever changing world and life. </p>
<p>Thank you for all of your work here, for all that you&#8217;ve shared with us, and for keeping it here for reference. I miss your voice but am delighted that you&#8217;re still writing.  All the best to you Molly!</p>
